## API Documentation

### `esri.directives` Module

The {@link esri.directives esri.directives} module includes reusable directives for map view, scene view, and related UI elements such as a home button.

### `esri.core` Module

The {@link esri.core esri.core} module includes services used by the directives in the {@link esri.directives esri.directives} module. These services can also be used directly by your own custom directives.
